```java
double sum(int n) {
    if (n % 2 == 0) return 0;
    double s = 0;
    for (int i = 3; i <= n; i += 2)
        s += 1.0 / (i * i);
    return 1 - s;
}
```

```java
double sum(int n) {
    if (n % 2 != 0) return 0;
    double s = 0;
    for (int i = 3; i <= n; i++)
        s += 1 / (i * i);
    return 1 - s;
}
```

```java
